text: Peter Cottrell (born 22 May 1957) is an English cricketer. He played ten first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club in 1979. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:British Universities cricketers
